#### Preconditions:

- Website Royal London (https://royallondonwatches.com/) is opened
- Stable internet connection


#### Test Case №1: Adding item to the cart
##### Steps:
- Scrolling the main page of the site to the first product
- Select the first item
- Press "Add to cart" on the product page.
- Click the cart icon in the menu at the top of the site.

##### Result: Item was added to cart
---------
#### Test Case №2: Proceed to Checkout
##### Steps:
- Click the cart icon in the menu at the top of the site.
- In the window that appears, click the "PROCEED TO CHECKOUT" button

##### Result: The checkout page is opened
---------
